{"tid":2365951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好困擾，商廈對面租戶走廊燒香問題","createTime":"2021-01-14T06:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:01:20.000Z","uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"deeb0d91bc3c010e70bf6770628c96596b9af137","tid":2365951,"uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"m<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXukJag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXukJag.jpg&h=f68ed7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無人知可以點搞？對面最近搬黎，一燒香就成個走廊都係，啲味仲攻埋入黎我單位。一返工就要硬食陣味，好撚辛苦。有冇人知可以點做？ 同對面傾過，佢地啲廢老好似聽唔明咁，問我幾時返工就嗰個時間唔燒，大佬呀幾時返同唔返根本唔係問題，你一燒啲味咪又係攻入晒黎。係唔係可以報消防？"},{"pid":"ad60c1eb41e6efe1670baf91bcca92f399d2d1d2","tid":2365951,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"換d香薰落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9bb1ff2206c4b314a443dec4fae985fce276bd","tid":2365951,"uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad60c1eb41e6efe1670baf91bcca92f399d2d1d2","tid":2365951,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"換d香薰落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推先，講真真係聞到好撚頭痛"},{"pid":"0f06b46bee1ef1483a7051482794bae6ae15d4e9","tid":2365951,"uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人救救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385cd7297a75305c629aa8f0706511e898f1c3ed","tid":2365951,"uid":133769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"空氣清新機幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0304adae40320b48a631b624592a65d2d6512a","tid":2365951,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"宗教自由<br />\n完<im